AND A LITTLE GIRL

04:15.338 --> 04:16.882
ACTUALLY REQUESTED ME.

04:16.924 --> 04:18.967
I'M GONNA BE

04:16.924 --> 04:18.967
A CELEBRITY MENTOR.

