WE'VE BEEN THROUGH

06:14.166 --> 06:16.793
SO MUCH ALREADY AND--

06:16.835 --> 06:18.419
Sweetie, if she doesn't want

06:16.835 --> 06:18.419
to be your friend,

06:18.461 --> 06:19.587
