AND THEN WE'LL GO GET

07:34.537 --> 07:36.081
SOME GELATO.

07:36.123 --> 07:39.376
OKAY, BUT WE GOTTA WAIT A WHILE

07:36.123 --> 07:39.376
BEFORE WE GET ON THE SUBWAY.

07:39.418 --> 07:41.502
THE GIRLS WHO BULLY ME

07:39.418 --> 07:41.502
ARE THERE NOW.

07:41.544 --> 07:42.921
YOU'RE GETTING BULLIED?

07:42.963 --> 07:45.506
THAT'S TERRIFIC.

07:42.963 --> 07:45.506
BULLYING'S HOT RIGHT NOW.

07:45.548 --> 07:46.925
DON'T YOU WORRY ABOUT

07:45.548 --> 07:46.925
A THING.

07:46.967 --> 07:48.676
I'M HERE TO MAKE

07:46.967 --> 07:48.676
ALL YOUR DREAMS COME TRUE.

07:48.718 --> 07:50.511
BUT I WANTED

07:48.718 --> 07:50.511
MY MARIO VAN PEEBLES DREAM

07:50.553 --> 07:51.305
TO COME TRUE.

07:51.346 --> 07:53.598
WELL, THAT ONE'S DEAD.

07:51.346 --> 07:53.598
COME ON.

07:57.560 --> 08:01.106
YOU KNOW, I DID

07:57.560 --> 08:01.106
A BULLYING P.S.A. BACK IN '99.

08:01.148 --> 08:02.899
WORST MAKEUP PERSON

08:01.148 --> 08:02.899
I EVER WORKED WITH.

08:02.941 --> 08:05.526
JUST UNTALENTED. IT WAS

08:02.941 --> 08:05.526
A NIGHTMARE. I HAD TO FIRE HER.

08:05.568 --> 08:07.321
(chime sounds)

08:07.362 --> 08:08.529
(woman over P.A.)

08:07.362 --> 08:08.529
ALL LARGE BAGS AND BACKPACKS...

08:08.571 --> 08:09.530
(speaks indistinctly)

08:09.572 --> 08:12.533
HEY, RELAX.

08:09.572 --> 08:12.533
I GOT YOUR BACK.

08:12.575 --> 08:14.244
(girl) HEY!

08:14.286 --> 08:15.912
(backpack thuds)

08:15.954 --> 08:17.538
(chime sounds)

08:15.954 --> 08:17.538
WHOA. THIS IS REAL.

08:17.580 --> 08:20.334
WHY YOU SO SHORT?

08:17.580 --> 08:20.334
WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOUR FACE?

08:20.375 --> 08:22.752
WHERE'S YOUR FRIEND AT?

08:22.794 --> 08:24.587
HE AIN'T HERE, BOO-BOO.

08:26.173 --> 08:28.049
HEY, CALL ME!

08:31.386 --> 08:34.222
COME ON, BARNEYS.

08:31.386 --> 08:34.222
I'M NOT IN THE MOOD.

08:31.386 --> 08:34.222
(click)

08:34.264 --> 08:37.476
(women laughing)

08:37.517 --> 08:39.019
OH! CHLOE, HI.

08:39.060 --> 08:40.479
THESE ARE MY NEW FRIENDS.

08:39.060 --> 08:40.479
(door closes)

08:40.520 --> 08:42.647
THIS IS ASHLEY, CARMEN,

08:40.520 --> 08:42.647
AND STEPHANIE.

08:42.689 --> 08:45.233
WE'VE BEEN HANGING OUT

08:42.689 --> 08:45.233
AT PILATES ALL WEEK.

08:45.275 --> 08:47.277
YEAH, PEOPLE CALL US

08:45.275 --> 08:47.277
THE HOTTIES 4 PILATES.

08:47.319 --> 08:48.362
(laughter)

08:48.403 --> 08:50.280
WE THOUGHT OF IT. I DID.

08:50.322 --> 08:52.573
WAIT. I'M SORRY.

08:50.322 --> 08:52.573
JUNE, WHO ARE THESE PEOPLE?

08:52.615 --> 08:54.493
I TOLD YOU. THEY'RE MY FRIENDS.

08:54.534 --> 08:56.577
WE ACTUALLY HAVE

08:54.534 --> 08:56.577
A LOT IN COMMON.

08:56.619 --> 08:57.787
(Stephanie, Carmen, and Ashley)

08:56.619 --> 08:57.787
MM-HMM.

08:57.829 --> 08:59.289
I MEAN, ASHLEY WORKS

08:57.829 --> 08:59.289
ON WALL STREET.

08:59.331 --> 09:02.376
WHEN I TOLD CARMEN THAT I LIKED

08:59.331 --> 09:02.376
FLAN, SHE NODDED IN AGREEMENT.

09:02.417 --> 09:04.585
AND STEPHANIE AND I BOTH LOOK

09:02.417 --> 09:04.585
EXACTLY THE SAME WAIST-DOWN

09:04.627 --> 09:06.380
IN OUR PILATES TIGHTS.

09:06.421 --> 09:07.506
WELL, NOT EXACTLY THE SAME.

09:07.547 --> 09:09.883
I HAVE THIS COOL

09:07.547 --> 09:09.883
KOKOPELLI TATTOO.

09:09.924 --> 09:12.469
HE'S THE FLUTE-PLAYING

09:09.924 --> 09:12.469
GOD OF LIFE.

09:12.511 --> 09:15.472
I JUST LOVE KNOWING THAT HE'S

09:12.511 --> 09:15.472
ALWAYS DOWN THERE, JAMMIN'.

09:15.514 --> 09:16.473
(laughs)

09:16.515 --> 09:17.807
I GOT HIM AT SURF CAMP

09:17.849 --> 09:19.893
AFTER I BROKE UP

09:17.849 --> 09:19.893
WITH MY BOYFRIEND FRANK.

09:19.934 --> 09:22.521
I ONLY NEEDED THREE IBUPROFEN.

09:22.562 --> 09:24.898
R-O-K. ROCK STAR!

09:24.939 --> 09:26.525
(laughter)

09:26.566 --> 09:29.736
OH! I JUST REALIZED.

09:26.566 --> 09:29.736
I HATE YOU.

09:30.653 --> 09:32.239
(scoffs)

09:32.280 --> 09:35.242
(whispers) YOU CAN'T BE RUDE

09:32.280 --> 09:35.242
TO MY FRIENDS!

09:35.283 --> 09:37.285
OH, COME ON, JUNE.

09:35.283 --> 09:37.285
THESE GIRLS ARE A JOKE.

09:37.327 --> 09:38.286
YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.

09:38.328 --> 09:40.205
OKAY,

09:38.328 --> 09:40.205
MAYBE THEY'RE NOT PERFECT,

09:40.247 --> 09:41.664
BUT YOU DON'T WANT

09:40.247 --> 09:41.664
TO BE MY FRIEND,

09:41.706 --> 09:42.832
AND THEY WANNA BE MY FRIENDS,

09:42.874 --> 09:45.210
AND I WANNA DRINK CAPPUCCINOS

09:42.874 --> 09:45.210
ON THE SIDEWALK.

09:45.252 --> 09:46.420
WHY DO YOU WANNA BE

09:45.252 --> 09:46.420
THEIR FRIEND?

09:46.461 --> 09:48.629
THEY'RE CATTY, OBNOXIOUS,

09:46.461 --> 09:48.629
AND IRRITATING,

09:48.671 --> 09:49.923
LIKE ALL GIRLS.

09:49.964 --> 09:51.550
"ALL GIRLS"? WHAT DO YOU--

09:49.964 --> 09:51.550
WHAT DO YOU EVEN MEAN?

09:51.591 --> 09:52.633
I MEAN, THOSE GIRLS

09:51.591 --> 09:52.633
ARE EXACTLY

09:52.675 --> 09:54.052
THE REASON WHY

09:52.675 --> 09:54.052
I DON'T HANG OUT WITH GIRLS.

09:54.094 --> 09:56.096
THEY'RE COMPETITIVE,

09:54.094 --> 09:56.096
THEY BACKSTAB,

09:56.137 --> 09:58.348
AND THEY POST GROUP PICTURES

09:56.137 --> 09:58.348
OF THEMSELVES ON FACEBOOK

09:58.390 --> 10:00.350
SO THEY CAN SHOW THE WORLD

09:58.390 --> 10:00.350
WHAT THEY LOOK LIKE IN A BIKINI.

10:00.392 --> 10:03.644
THAT WAS A TANKINI, AND I WAS

10:00.392 --> 10:03.644
TAGGED IN THAT PHOTO.

10:00.392 --> 10:03.644
(bottle cap clatters)

10:03.686 --> 10:05.313
LOOK, I JUST PREFER

10:03.686 --> 10:05.313
TO HANG OUT WITH DUDES.

10:05.355 --> 10:07.566
THEY SAY WHAT THEY MEAN,

10:05.355 --> 10:07.566
THEY LIKE TO HAVE FUN,

10:07.607 --> 10:09.568
AND IN A PINCH,

10:07.607 --> 10:09.568
THEY HAVE A PENIS.

10:09.609 --> 10:10.902
(door opens)

10:12.612 --> 10:14.906
STUPID SHIRTS.

10:16.283 --> 10:17.658
AWESOME SHIRT.

10:19.286 --> 10:21.662
THAT'S HOW YOU SHOULD DRESS,

10:19.286 --> 10:21.662
LADIES.

10:21.704 --> 10:24.040
PAY ATTENTION.

10:24.082 --> 10:27.544
(Schubert's "Valses

10:24.082 --> 10:27.544
sentimentales, Op. 50" playing)

10:27.586 --> 10:29.463
(sighs)

10:29.504 --> 10:30.671
(door opens)

10:30.713 --> 10:32.673
(sighs) THANK GOD YOU'RE HERE.

10:32.715 --> 10:33.716
I HAVE TO TELL YOU ABOUT

10:33.758 --> 10:35.760
THIS HELLISH GIRL EXPERIENCE

10:33.758 --> 10:35.760
I JUST HAD.

10:35.802 --> 10:37.137
YEAH,

10:35.802 --> 10:37.137
I'M HAVING A PROBLEM, TOO.

10:37.178 --> 10:38.346
IT'S KIM,

10:37.178 --> 10:38.346
MY PUBLICITY PROJECT.

10:38.388 --> 10:40.557
I FEEL AWFUL. I ABANDONED HER

10:38.388 --> 10:40.557
IN A MOMENT OF CRISIS.

10:40.599 --> 10:42.183
UGH! NOT YOU, TOO!

10:42.225 --> 10:44.394
STICK A TAMPON IN IT

10:42.225 --> 10:44.394
AND CALL YOUR MOM.

10:44.436 --> 10:47.981
THESE NEW FRIENDS OF JUNE'S

10:44.436 --> 10:47.981
ARE SO HORRIBLE.

10:48.022 --> 10:49.983
SHE'S REALLY SCRAPING

10:48.022 --> 10:49.983
THE BOTTOM OF THE BARREL.

10:50.024 --> 10:51.776
WELL, NOBODY LIKES

10:50.024 --> 10:51.776
TO BE ALONE.

10:51.818 --> 10:54.070
I'D RATHER BE ALONE THAN BE

10:51.818 --> 10:54.070
WITH THAT GIRL STEPHANIE.

10:54.112 --> 10:56.906
SHE'S THE WORST.

10:54.112 --> 10:56.906
SHE THINKS SHE'S THE QUEEN BEE.

10:56.948 --> 10:58.783
YOU KNOW, ONE OF THOSE GIRLS

10:56.948 --> 10:58.783
WHO ONLY TALKS ABOUT HERSELF

10:58.825 --> 11:00.785
AND GOES AROUND WITH AN ARMY

10:58.825 --> 11:00.785
OF LITTLE PINK GROUPIES.

11:00.827 --> 11:03.704
"QUEEN BEE"?

11:00.827 --> 11:03.704
SO THERE'S A POWER DYNAMIC, HUH?

11:03.746 --> 11:05.290
YEAH, AND IT'S DISGUSTING.

11:05.332 --> 11:07.000
IT'S SOMETHING YOU WOULD

11:05.332 --> 11:07.000
NEVER HAVE WITH A GUY FRIEND.

11:07.041 --> 11:10.128
I'M LEAVING

11:07.041 --> 11:10.128
AND I'M TAKING THIS.

11:11.129 --> 11:12.755
AND THIS.

11:14.757 --> 11:16.717
(siren wailing, horn honks)

11:16.759 --> 11:18.637
♪♪♪

11:18.677 --> 11:20.721
HEY, BILLY.

11:18.677 --> 11:20.721
I'LL HAVE THE USUAL.

11:20.763 --> 11:21.889
ACTUALLY, CHLOE,

11:21.931 --> 11:24.976
YOUR FRIENDS ALREADY ORDERED

11:21.931 --> 11:24.976
A DRINK FOR YOU.

11:26.561 --> 11:27.895
GIRL GRENADE!

11:26.561 --> 11:27.895
AAH!

11:27.937 --> 11:29.606
(Stephanie laughs)

11:27.937 --> 11:29.606
HI!

11:29.648 --> 11:31.732
(chuckles) SO I'VE BEEN THINKING

11:29.648 --> 11:31.732
ABOUT WHAT YOU SAID

11:31.774 --> 11:33.234
ABOUT NOT HAVING

11:31.774 --> 11:33.234
ANY FEMALE FRIENDS,

11:33.276 --> 11:36.946
AND I REALIZED IT'S JUST BECAUSE

11:33.276 --> 11:36.946
YOU HAVEN'T GIVEN THEM A CHANCE.

11:36.988 --> 11:39.115
FORGET IT, JUNE.

11:36.988 --> 11:39.115
COME ON.

11:39.157 --> 11:40.741
YOU CAN'T HATE SOMETHING IF YOU

11:39.157 --> 11:40.741
HAVEN'T EVEN TRIED IT BEFORE.

11:40.783 --> 11:41.742
PLEASE?

11:41.784 --> 11:43.911
(sighs deeply)

11:43.953 --> 11:46.331
OH! OOH!

11:43.953 --> 11:46.331
(giggling)

11:46.373 --> 11:48.833
OKAY, THE FIRST RULE

11:46.373 --> 11:48.833
OF GIRLFRIENDS--

11:48.875 --> 11:50.669
HMM?

11:48.875 --> 11:50.669
YOU DO NOT TALK

11:48.875 --> 11:50.669
ABOUT GIRLFRIENDS.

11:50.709 --> 11:52.753
(laughs) MOVIE REFERENCE!

11:52.795 --> 11:54.464
OH, THAT'S FROM "LA BAMBA"!

11:54.506 --> 11:58.134
WHAT? NO, CARMEN. NOT

11:54.506 --> 11:58.134
EVERYTHING'S FROM "LA BAMBA"!

11:58.176 --> 11:59.469
♪♪♪

11:59.511 --> 12:01.762
MY DOCTOR SAYS I CAN'T LOSE

11:59.511 --> 12:01.762
ANY MORE WEIGHT.

12:01.804 --> 12:03.390
I'M IN THE RED ZONE.

12:03.431 --> 12:05.766
I EAT AND I EAT...

12:03.431 --> 12:05.766
NOTHING. I'M CURSED.

12:05.808 --> 12:07.268
(slurps drink)

12:07.310 --> 12:09.646
I MEAN, CARMEN, YOU'RE SO LUCKY

12:07.310 --> 12:09.646
YOU DON'T HAVE THIS.

12:09.688 --> 12:11.231
(slurps) WHAT THE HELL?

12:11.272 --> 12:13.774
I'VE HAD, LIKE, EIGHT OF THESE

12:11.272 --> 12:13.774
AND I DON'T EVEN FEEL BUZZED.

12:13.816 --> 12:15.776
OH, THAT'S BECAUSE

12:13.816 --> 12:15.776
THERE'S NO ALCOHOL IN THERE.

12:15.818 --> 12:17.862
WE DON'T WANNA GET

12:15.818 --> 12:17.862
DRINKY WRINKLES.

12:17.904 --> 12:20.781
SO I'M JUST DRINKING JUICE,

12:17.904 --> 12:20.781
LIKE A KID?

12:20.823 --> 12:22.283
MM-HMM.

12:20.823 --> 12:22.283
(glasses shatter)

12:22.325 --> 12:25.078
WHAT IS HAPPENING AT THIS TABLE

12:22.325 --> 12:25.078
IS RIDICULOUS.

12:25.119 --> 12:27.080
STEPHANIE,

12:25.119 --> 12:27.080
STOP ABBREVIATING WORDS.

12:27.121 --> 12:28.789
YOU DON'T HAVE A JOB.

12:27.121 --> 12:28.789
YOU HAVE THE TIME.

12:28.831 --> 12:30.083
ASHLEY, YOU'RE JUST

12:28.831 --> 12:30.083
TELLING STEPHANIE

12:30.124 --> 12:32.293
SHE DID THE RIGHT THING

12:30.124 --> 12:32.293
BY KICKING FRANK TO THE CURB

12:32.335 --> 12:33.961
BECAUSE YOU OBVIOUSLY

12:32.335 --> 12:33.961
WANNA SLEEP WITH HIM.

12:34.003 --> 12:35.672
AND, CARMEN,

12:34.003 --> 12:35.672
FOR THE LOVE OF GOD,

12:35.714 --> 12:38.174
CAN YOU STOP QUOTING "LA BAMBA"

12:35.714 --> 12:38.174
FOR ONE SECOND?

12:38.216 --> 12:41.302
"EVERYTHING'S RITCHIE, RITCHIE!

12:38.216 --> 12:41.302
WHAT ABOUT BOB?!"

12:41.344 --> 12:42.262
(laughs)

12:42.303 --> 12:44.805
YOU'VE GOT US PEGGED,

12:42.303 --> 12:44.805
DON'T YOU?

12:44.847 --> 12:47.183
YOU THINK THAT BY ACTING TOUGH

12:44.847 --> 12:47.183
AND REJECTING US

12:47.225 --> 12:49.603
BEFORE WE REJECT YOU

12:47.225 --> 12:49.603
THAT YOU CAN PROTECT YOURSELF.

12:49.644 --> 12:51.896
YOU'RE JUST SCARED THAT

12:49.644 --> 12:51.896
SOMEONE'S GONNA SEE THE  REAL  YOU

12:51.938 --> 12:53.314
AND FIND OUT THAT

12:53.356 --> 12:54.691
YOU'RE NOT AS INTERESTING

12:53.356 --> 12:54.691
AS YOU THINK YOU ARE.

12:54.733 --> 12:56.984
WELL YOU'RE NOT AS SKINNY

12:54.733 --> 12:56.984
AS YOU THINK YOU ARE.

12:57.026 --> 12:59.529
SHOULDN'T YOU BE DANCING

12:57.026 --> 12:59.529
IN A GLASS BOOTH SOMEWHERE?

12:59.571 --> 13:00.821
NO. YOUR MOM TOOK MY SHIFT.

13:00.863 --> 13:03.324
MY MOM PASSED AWAY

13:00.863 --> 13:03.324
TWO YEARS AGO.

13:03.366 --> 13:05.285
WELL, YOU LOOK LIKE

13:03.366 --> 13:05.285
DONALD SUTHERLAND.

13:05.326 --> 13:06.411
YES, THAT'S RIGHT.

13:06.453 --> 13:09.539
THERE'S ONLY ROOM FOR ONE BITCH

13:06.453 --> 13:09.539
IN APARTMENT 23.

13:09.581 --> 13:12.292
DID YOU GUYS TRY THESE NACHOS?

13:09.581 --> 13:12.292
THEY ARE YUMMO!

13:12.333 --> 13:14.877
(mouth full) I LOVE 'EM.

13:12.333 --> 13:14.877
THEY'RE GREAT. (crunching)

13:14.919 --> 13:16.921
OKAY, I'M OUT OF HERE.

13:16.963 --> 13:19.090
JUNE, I'LL PICK YOU UP TOMORROW

13:16.963 --> 13:19.090
FOR PILATES.

13:19.132 --> 13:21.008
WE CAN DISCUSS FINDING YOU

13:19.132 --> 13:21.008
ANOTHER ROOMMATE

13:21.050 --> 13:23.344
WHO ISN'T A TOTAL PSYCHO.

13:26.180 --> 13:28.849
SO WHO HAS THOUGHTS

13:26.180 --> 13:28.849
ON ANNE HATHAWAY?

13:28.891 --> 13:30.017
HEY, STEPHANIE FORGOT

13:28.891 --> 13:30.017
HER JACKET.

13:30.059 --> 13:31.936
OH. I'LL GIVE IT TO HER.

13:31.978 --> 13:34.981
WE HAVE UNFINISHED BUSINESS.

13:37.776 --> 13:39.860
HEY, STEPHANIE, IT'S JUNE AGAIN.

13:39.902 --> 13:42.739
PILATES STARTED

13:39.902 --> 13:42.739
OVER AN HOUR AGO.

13:42.781 --> 13:43.782
WHERE ARE YOU?

13:43.822 --> 13:45.866
GIVE ME A CALL. BYE.

13:43.822 --> 13:45.866
(beep)

13:45.908 --> 13:48.161
I DON'T THINK SHE'S COMING.

13:45.908 --> 13:48.161
(turns on TV)

13:48.202 --> 13:50.455
...ANOTHER GIRL WAS FOUND

13:48.202 --> 13:50.455
MURDERED IN THE PARK.

13:50.497 --> 13:52.039
THE UNIDENTIFIED VICTIM

13:50.497 --> 13:52.039
WAS FOUND

13:52.081 --> 13:53.458
CLUTCHING A PILATES MAT

13:53.500 --> 13:55.876
AND HAS A TATTOO ON HER ANKLE

13:53.500 --> 13:55.876
OF KOKOPELLI.

13:55.918 --> 13:57.754
OH, MY GOD.

13:55.918 --> 13:57.754
(man) UH, IT'S VERY DISTURBING.

13:57.796 --> 14:00.674
IT'S STEPHANIE!

13:57.796 --> 14:00.674
UM, THE LADIES APPEAR TO BE

13:57.796 --> 14:00.674
ALL AGES AND ALL RANGES...

14:00.715 --> 14:03.134
OHH.

14:00.715 --> 14:03.134
...OF WEIGHT, COLOR,

14:00.715 --> 14:03.134
AND CREED...

14:03.176 --> 14:06.680
ROUGH NIGHT.

14:03.176 --> 14:06.680
A LOT OF BAD CHOICES.

14:06.721 --> 14:08.723
...THIS MAY NOT END.

14:06.721 --> 14:08.723
THIS MAY BE JUST THE BEGINNING.

14:08.765 --> 14:09.766
(door closes)

14:14.813 --> 14:16.063
UH, WE'VE JUST WITNESSED--

14:16.105 --> 14:17.565
(changes channel)

14:16.105 --> 14:17.565
WOW. IT'S ON EVERY CHANNEL.

14:17.607 --> 14:19.818
SHOCKING. I HAVEN'T PAID

14:17.607 --> 14:19.818
FOR CABLE IN THREE YEARS.

14:19.859 --> 14:21.695
HOW ARE WE STILL GETTING TV?

14:21.736 --> 14:24.113
SO, UM...

14:24.155 --> 14:26.783
WHY ARE YOU WEARING

14:24.155 --> 14:26.783
STEPHANIE'S JACKET?

14:26.825 --> 14:29.910
OH, I TRIED TO GIVE IT BACK

14:26.825 --> 14:29.910
TO HER BUT I COULDN'T FIND HER.

14:29.952 --> 14:32.997
WE HAVE UNFINISHED BUSINESS.

14:34.957 --> 14:37.918
LATER, STUPID!

14:37.960 --> 14:38.919
GO!

14:38.961 --> 14:40.213
SO...

14:38.961 --> 14:40.213
(TV playing indistinctly)

14:40.254 --> 14:42.006
WHAT DID YOU DO

14:40.254 --> 14:42.006
FOR THE REST OF THE NIGHT?

14:42.048 --> 14:45.134
NOTHING. I JUST WENT TO JAMES'

14:42.048 --> 14:45.134
TO WATCH TV.

14:46.260 --> 14:49.597
WHY?

14:46.260 --> 14:49.597
WHAT ARE YOU INSINUATING?

14:49.639 --> 14:51.932
NOTHING...

14:51.974 --> 14:53.100
UNLESS THERE IS SOMETHING

14:53.142 --> 14:55.978
THAT YOU FEEL LIKE YOU NEED

14:53.142 --> 14:55.978
TO TELL ME.

14:59.982 --> 15:01.108
KISS!

15:01.150 --> 15:04.320
NO. I'M MAD AT HER.

15:04.362 --> 15:06.030
W--

15:06.072 --> 15:08.783
I CAN'T BELIEVE JUNE THINKS

15:06.072 --> 15:08.783
I KILLED HER DUMB FRIEND!

15:08.825 --> 15:09.950
(James) That's crazy.

15:09.992 --> 15:11.327
SO DID YOU?

15:11.369 --> 15:12.995
WHAT? NO! I WAS WITH YOU.

15:13.037 --> 15:14.372
(snoring)

15:14.414 --> 15:15.956
THAT'S IT.

15:14.414 --> 15:15.956
THAT'S THE PERFECT LOOK FOR KIM.

15:15.998 --> 15:17.958
(turns off TV)

15:15.998 --> 15:17.958
IS THIS COUCH A POD?

15:18.000 --> 15:21.880
BECAUSE WE, SIR,

15:18.000 --> 15:21.880
ARE TWO PEAS IN IT.

15:21.921 --> 15:23.047
JUNE BEING SUSPICIOUS OF ME

